Samba VFS modules for GlusterFS

To build:

1.) Download and unpack a Samba source tree.
2.) ./autogen.sh
3.) ./configure --with-samba-source=/path/to/samba_dir/source3
4.) make

To install:

    make install

Clean-up commands:

1.) make clean
    Removes build files.

2.) make distclean
    Removes any files generated from all the above commands, including the
    Makefile.

